 That is, we will solve: 
\begin_inset Formula \[
G(\vec{y}_{m},\vec{x}')=0\approx\ln|\vec{y}_{m}-\vec{x}'|+\sum_{n=1}^{N}\sigma_{n}\ln|\vec{y}_{m}-\vec{x}_{n}|\]

